1
00:00:00,041 --> 00:00:02,168
The feelings you're experiencing right now,

2
00:00:02,168 --> 00:00:04,170
you're just confusing them.

3
00:00:04,212 --> 00:00:05,463
Because we've known each other for so long,

4
00:00:05,463 --> 00:00:08,091
you're just mistaking those feelings.

5
00:00:08,133 --> 00:00:10,301
Why do you get to decide that, Teacher?

6
00:00:10,301 --> 00:00:11,761
They're my feelings.

7
00:00:11,928 --> 00:00:14,556
I know my own heart best.

8
00:00:14,848 --> 00:00:16,766
I like you, Teacher.

9
00:00:16,766 --> 00:00:19,144
For the past three years, constantly.

10
00:00:20,311 --> 00:00:22,480
I've only had eyes for you.

11
00:00:25,191 --> 00:00:28,361
Yoon Jaeon.

12
00:00:28,361 --> 00:00:31,948
Playing house with a kid...

13
00:00:32,699 --> 00:00:35,076
I have no intention of doing that.

14
00:00:47,005 --> 00:00:48,423
I'm not a kid anymore.

15
00:00:48,423 --> 00:00:52,177
You said it yourself, Teacher.

16
00:00:52,427 --> 00:00:56,431
So I'm going to like you as much as I want now.

17
00:01:13,823 --> 00:01:15,408
You're practically inside your phone.

18
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:17,327
He's not replying.

19
00:01:17,327 --> 00:01:20,330
(Asks if he can come see him, but Hyunseo doesn't reply)

20
00:01:26,628 --> 00:01:28,713
You have to give him time to reply, right?

21
00:01:29,756 --> 00:01:32,175
I just don't know what to do.

22
00:01:33,009 --> 00:01:35,178
A kid like you, almost ten years younger...

23
00:01:35,178 --> 00:01:36,179
do you think you'd catch his eye?

24
00:01:36,304 --> 00:01:37,806
Hey, enough with the "kid" stuff!

25
00:01:37,806 --> 00:01:39,682
How is a twenty-year-old a kid?

26
00:01:39,891 --> 00:01:41,101
I'm old enough to know everything.

27
00:01:42,435 --> 00:01:44,020
To the Professor,

28
00:01:44,020 --> 00:01:46,356
you probably just look like a little kid.

29
00:01:49,651 --> 00:01:51,903
(Hyunseo still hasn't replied)

30
00:01:54,906 --> 00:01:56,533
Then act like an adult.

31
00:01:57,117 --> 00:01:57,909
An adult?

32
00:01:58,409 --> 00:02:00,912
Stop throwing tantrums asking him to date you,

33
00:02:01,037 --> 00:02:02,872
and try approaching him seriously.

34
00:02:05,708 --> 00:02:06,709
Forget it.

35
00:02:06,709 --> 00:02:08,253
What did I even expect from you?

36
00:02:15,051 --> 00:02:17,554
Seriously, how can he be so coldhearted?

37
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:19,139
Who?

38
00:02:21,850 --> 00:02:23,434
This means he wants me to come over, right?

39
00:02:24,561 --> 00:02:26,354
(Hyunseo texted, "Don't come.")

40
00:02:26,521 --> 00:02:27,564
Where?

41
00:02:27,981 --> 00:02:29,524
Where does he want you to come?

42
00:02:36,447 --> 00:02:39,159
He just does whatever he wants.

43
00:02:50,128 --> 00:02:51,629
I told you not to come.

44
00:02:52,046 --> 00:02:55,133
I came because I thought that meant "come."

45
00:02:55,133 --> 00:02:56,301
You haven't eaten, right?

46
00:02:58,469 --> 00:02:59,596
I'm not hungry.

47
00:02:59,888 --> 00:03:03,308
Just have one bite, at least for the effort I put into bringing it.

48
00:03:27,665 --> 00:03:29,167
Look at you eating so well.

49
00:03:29,167 --> 00:03:30,251
Have some more.

50
00:03:30,251 --> 00:03:31,044
Should I feed you?

51
00:03:32,253 --> 00:03:33,546
Just leave it and go.

52
00:03:33,546 --> 00:03:34,756
I'll eat it later.

53
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:38,468
If I say I like you,

54
00:03:38,468 --> 00:03:40,511
shouldn't you say "Thank you" and date me?

55
00:03:40,887 --> 00:03:42,805
I like you so much, Teacher.

56
00:03:43,598 --> 00:03:46,768
If you're going to say nonsense, just leave.

57
00:03:46,935 --> 00:03:48,811
You're distracting me.

58
00:04:04,744 --> 00:04:06,704
Do you really hate me that much, Teacher?

59
00:04:06,913 --> 00:04:08,498
I never said I hated you.

60
00:04:09,457 --> 00:04:10,458
What?

61
00:04:11,042 --> 00:04:12,752
When did I say I hated you?

62
00:04:13,294 --> 00:04:15,296
I just told you not to like me.

63
00:04:18,174 --> 00:04:20,718
Then why did you quit tutoring me?

64
00:04:20,843 --> 00:04:23,471
Wasn't it because I confessed my feelings?

65
00:04:25,265 --> 00:04:27,684
I just didn't want you to go through the same experience I did.

66
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:31,145
Unrequited love...

67
00:04:31,145 --> 00:04:34,023
It's a terrible thing to go through.

68
00:04:34,023 --> 00:04:36,901
I thought your feelings would naturally fade if I disappeared.

69
00:04:40,363 --> 00:04:42,115
Things like unrequited love...

70
00:04:44,033 --> 00:04:45,618
Don't do it.

71
00:04:49,330 --> 00:04:53,793
Do you think the heart works like that?

72
00:04:53,793 --> 00:04:55,628
Even you couldn't do it either.

73
00:05:01,843 --> 00:05:03,845
When someone disappears from your sight...

74
00:05:03,845 --> 00:05:05,596
you know perfectly well it only makes you miss them more.

75
00:05:12,937 --> 00:05:14,272
Huh?

76
00:05:14,272 --> 00:05:15,565
Teacher?

77
00:05:16,065 --> 00:05:17,775
Yujun.

78
00:05:18,151 --> 00:05:20,528
I have no feelings for you, Sunbae.

79
00:05:21,821 --> 00:05:26,034
Please just remain a good Sunbae to me from now on.

80
00:05:27,952 --> 00:05:29,370
Is it really a no?

81
00:05:30,496 --> 00:05:31,748
Yes.

82
00:05:32,332 --> 00:05:34,417
I'm sorry if I gave you mixed signals.

83
00:05:55,521 --> 00:05:57,440
Is that him?

84
00:05:57,440 --> 00:06:00,651
The guy you said you liked?

85
00:06:00,651 --> 00:06:04,405
But there's someone else next to him...

86
00:06:08,534 --> 00:06:10,119
Teacher.

87
00:06:11,371 --> 00:06:13,664
You're distracted again, aren't you?

88
00:06:15,625 --> 00:06:17,418
You said you have someone you like, right?

89
00:06:21,089 --> 00:06:21,506
Yeah.

90
00:06:22,256 --> 00:06:24,008
So focus on your studies.

91
00:06:25,802 --> 00:06:27,929
But he had someone else next to him?

92
00:06:27,929 --> 00:06:29,806
And you still liked him despite that?

93
00:06:30,306 --> 00:06:32,934
I don't know what you're talking about.

94
00:06:33,309 --> 00:06:35,186
I saw everything.

95
00:06:35,353 --> 00:06:37,730
You getting rejected...

96
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:39,732
And that other person next to him...

97
00:06:48,241 --> 00:06:50,451
What is it you want to say?

98
00:06:53,955 --> 00:06:56,124
I like you, Teacher.
